title: State of the Dead
description:
Spiritualism is taking the world by storm. Many don't have an understanding as to what happens when we die. 

The world is taught that we can see our dead loved ones and even speak to them.

 The Word of God reveals to us the truth in this case. 

We must not be like king Saul and seek the dead or even seek the dead through so called spiritual readers and such. 

People are being highly deceived due to their lack of knowledge. Many claim they the can speak to Mary or the other Saints to get their prayers answered which is false. 


Please watch the video and see what the Word of God reveals to us. Thank you
